    "Correspondingly, Borenstein and Howard (2021) scrutinize the ethical implications of Artificial Intelligence technologies.",
    "AI is transforming the world with both benefits and risks.",
    "To prepare future AI professionals and stakeholders, it's crucial to integrate AI ethics into education.",
    "This paper outlines AI ethics approaches and provides recommendations for AI ethics education.",
    "In addition, Knox (2020) explores the intricate relationship between government policy and private-sector engagement in AI education in China."
